      • isAutocastSelectionNeeded

        public boolean isAutocastSelectionNeeded()
        A spell needs to be selected before autocast starts using that spell if returns true. If a spell was previously set, then that spell is used until another is selected if this method returns true.
        Returns:
        true if the selection window was opened and a spell is needing selected. This can return true even if its not displayed (e.g. another tab is selected).
